dataIdInfo.envirDesc: Microsoft Windows Server 2016 Technical Preview Version 10.0 (Build 20348) ; Esri ArcGIS 13.1.0.41833
dataIdInfo.idPurp: Rice field watershed groupings Used to determine distances to nearest fish bearing stream
dataIdInfo.idAbs:
Dataset started with HUC 10 shapefile from USGS, and split in locations as necessary to more accurately define distances to the nearest outfall return location or distance to nearest salmon rearing stream.

Fields:

HUC10 = Hydrologic Unit Code (HUC) from USGS

Name = Name of the HUC watershed unit

group_id = group identification given for rice drainage study

return_id = watershed drainage return location for which flow distance is calculated

searchKeys.keyword: MWD Rice Field Drainage watershed groups

attrdomv.udom: Sequential unique whole numbers that are automatically generated.

attr.attrdef: Area of feature in internal units squared.

attrdomv.udom: Positive real numbers that are automatically generated.
